TurnOnObject_0:
(:action TurnOnObject_0
        :parameters (?toolobject - object ?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object)

        :precondition (and 
		(objectType ?toolobject LightSwitchType)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
		(toggleable ?o)
		(holds ?a ?toolobject)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(isToggled ?o)
		)
)

ThrowObject_0:
(:action ThrowObject_0
        :parameters (?toolobject - object ?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object)

        :precondition (and 
		(objectType ?toolobject BaseballBatType)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
		(holds ?a ?toolobject)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(not (objectAtLocation ?o ?l))
		(not (holds ?a ?o))
		)
)

		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
		(holds ?a ?o)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(not (objectAtLocation ?o ?l))
		(inReceptacle ?o ?toolreceptacle)
		)
)
